Smith DS(1), Krygiel J, Nease RF Jr, Sumner W 2nd, Catalona WJ.

Author information:
(1)Yale University School of Medicine, New Haven, Connecticut, USA.

PURPOSE: We used utility assessment to evaluate patient preferences for current 
urinary and sexual function after radical prostatectomy.
